This is a list of the [[Sites of Special Scientific Interest]] (SSSIs) in [[Warwickshire]]. [[English Nature]], the designating body for SSSIs in [[England]], uses the [[Metropolitan and non-metropolitan counties of England|1974–1996 county system]]. The majority of these sites are locally managed by the [[Warwickshire Wildlife Trust]].
For other counties, see [[List of SSSIs by Area of Search]].
