The [[Bayer designation]] '''Tau Aquarii''' (τ Aqr / τ Aquarii) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Aquarius (constellation)|Aquarius]]: * [[Tau¹ Aquarii|τ<sup>1</sup> Aquarii]] * [[Tau² Aquarii|τ<sup>2</sup> Aquarii]] They are separated by 0.65° on the sky.
All of them were member of asterism 羽林軍 (''Yǔ Lín Jūn''), ''Palace Guard'', ''[[Encampment (Chinese constellation)|Encampment]]'' mansion.<ref>{{zh icon}} [http://aeea.nmns.edu.tw/2006/0607/ap060707.html AEEA (Activities of Exhibition and Education in Astronomy) 天文教育資訊網 2006 年 7 月 7 日]</ref>
